title: Texans rule out Benardrick McKinney (concussion), Kareem Jackson (ankle)
text:
Published By: Houston Chronicle Sports - Today 
Texans rookie inside linebacker Benardrick McKinney has been ruled out of the game with a concussion sustained in the second quarter....
